content: I'll have to check some of those out. I'm really in the mood for something with great characters and humor. By the way, I've been on a bit of a media kick lately - I just watched the play "Hamilton" on Disney+ a few weeks ago and loved it, and before that, I binge-watched all six seasons of Schitt's Creek on Netflix in two weeks. Musicals and TV shows with great characters have really been my thing lately.
